-+ * - Unimplemented methods return `{ data: null, errors: [] }`
-+ * - UI-critical methods have `with*Result()` builders for preset returns
-+ *
-+ * Per Constitution P4: full fake, not mocks.
-+ * Per DYK-I2: Proxy cuts from ~600 lines to ~200.
-+ */
-+
